      • addInterceptor

        public NetworkService addInterceptor(okhttp3.Interceptor interceptor)
        add Interceptor. 
         
 NetworkService service = NetworkService();
 service.ServerUrl("https://mpc.pentasecurity.com")
        .addInterceptor(chain -> {
          Request original = chain.request();
          Request.Builder builder1 = original.newBuilder()
            .header("Authorization", "dGsdscs==");
          Request request = builder1.build();
          return chain.proceed(request);
        });
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        NetworkService this
